sub_title: Project Manager at Netherlands Foreign Investment Agency
summary: International professional promoting foreign direct investment in the Netherlands at the Netherlands Foreign Investment Agency (NFIA) within the Dutch Ministry of Economic Affairs and Climate.  Experience in export trade development at the trade sections of the American and British Embassies in the Netherlands, as well as the Dutch Enterprise Agency (RVO) within the Dutch Ministry of Economic Affairs and Climate. Bilingual in English (native) and Dutch.  Lived and worked in Australia, the Netherlands, UK and France.
